{"an4.23:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.23 ","an4.23:0.2":"3. Uruvelavagga ","an4.23:0.3":"Lokasutta ","an4.23:1.1":"“Loko, bhikkhave, tathagatena abhisambuddho. ","an4.23:1.2":"Lokasma tathagato visamyutto. ","an4.23:1.3":"Lokasamudayo, bhikkhave, tathagatena abhisambuddho. ","an4.23:1.4":"Lokasamudayo tathagatassa pahino. ","an4.23:1.5":"Lokanirodho, bhikkhave, tathagatena abhisambuddho. ","an4.23:1.6":"Lokanirodho tathagatassa sacchikato. ","an4.23:1.7":"Lokanirodhagamini patipada, bhikkhave, tathagatena abhisambuddha. ","an4.23:1.8":"Lokanirodhagamini patipada tathagatassa bhavita. ","an4.23:2.1":"Yam, bhikkhave, sadevakassa lokassa samarakassa sabrahmakassa sassamanabrahmaniya pajaya sadevamanussaya dittham sutam mutam vinnatam pattam pariyesitam anuvicaritam manasa, sabbam tam tathagatena abhisambuddham. ","an4.23:2.2":"Tasma ‘tathagato’ti vuccati. ","an4.23:3.1":"Yanca, bhikkhave, rattim tathagato anuttaram sammasambodhim abhisambujjhati yanca rattim anupadisesaya nibbanadhatuya parinibbayati, yam etasmim antare bhasati lapati niddisati sabbam tam tatheva hoti, no annatha. ","an4.23:3.2":"Tasma ‘tathagato’ti vuccati. ","an4.23:4.1":"Yathavadi, bhikkhave, tathagato tathakari, yathakari tathavadi. ","an4.23:4.2":"Iti yathavadi tathakari, yathakari tathavadi. ","an4.23:4.3":"Tasma ‘tathagato’ti vuccati. ","an4.23:5.1":"Sadevake, bhikkhave, loke samarake sabrahmake sassamanabrahmaniya pajaya sadevamanussaya tathagato abhibhu anabhibhuto annadatthu daso vasavatti. ","an4.23:5.2":"Tasma ‘tathagato’ti vuccati. ","an4.23:6.1":"Sabbam lokam abhinnaya, ","an4.23:6.2":"sabbam loke yathatatham; ","an4.23:6.3":"Sabbam lokam visamyutto, ","an4.23:6.4":"sabbaloke anupayo. ","an4.23:7.1":"Sa ve sabbabhibhu dhiro, ","an4.23:7.2":"sabbaganthappamocano; ","an4.23:7.3":"Phuttha’ssa parama santi, ","an4.23:7.4":"nibbanam akutobhayam. ","an4.23:8.1":"Esa khinasavo buddho, ","an4.23:8.2":"anigho chinnasamsayo; ","an4.23:8.3":"Sabbakammakkhayam patto, ","an4.23:8.4":"vimutto upadhisankhaye. ","an4.23:9.1":"Esa so bhagava buddho, ","an4.23:9.2":"esa siho anuttaro; ","an4.23:9.3":"Sadevakassa lokassa, ","an4.23:9.4":"brahmacakkam pavattayi. ","an4.23:10.1":"Iti deva manussa ca, ","an4.23:10.2":"ye buddham saranam gata; ","an4.23:10.3":"Sangamma tam namassanti, ","an4.23:10.4":"mahantam vitasaradam. ","an4.23:11.1":"Danto damayatam settho, ","an4.23:11.2":"santo samayatam isi; ","an4.23:11.3":"Mutto mocayatam aggo, ","an4.23:11.4":"tinno tarayatam varo. ","an4.23:12.1":"Iti hetam namassanti, ","an4.23:12.2":"mahantam vitasaradam; ","an4.23:12.3":"Sadevakasmim lokasmim, ","an4.23:12.4":"natthi me patipuggalo”ti. ","an4.23:12.5":"Tatiyam. "}